    "ACCESS TO DATA: The Principal Investigator (PI) will oversee the storage and maintenance of all data gathered throughout or after the study.",
    "The PI will retain access to the ultimate trial dataset, which will be shared in a de-identified format upon formal request, specifically for research and publication purposes only.",
    "ANCILLARY AND POST-TRIAL CARE: In the event of any occurrences resulting in harm from trial participation, care will be provided to the study subjects by the Principal Investigator (PI) following the policies outlined by Ravi Nair Physiotherapy College and DMIHER.",
    "DISSEMINATION POLICY: Data collected during or after the study will only be utilized for academic and researchrelated purposes culminating in a publication in a reputedjournal.",
